 elevado</b> de la infraestructura o instalación afectada. Se requiere permiso del titular <font color=\"#009fda\"><a href='https://www.adif.es/solicitud-de-actuaciones-en-zona-de-afeccion-del-ferrocarril'  target='_blank'>ADIF</a></font>.</p>","type":"CONDITIONAL","geometry":[[40.41324311100004,-3.703688315999898],[40.41331800000006,-3.7038968759999307],[40.41340654700008,-3.7040960689998883],[40.413508069000045,-3.7042843649999213],[40.413621791000025,-3.7044603239999105],[40.41374684200008,-3.704622595999922],[40.413882261000026,-3.7047699369999236],[40.41402701100003,-3.7049012189999075],[40.414179983000054,-3.7050154329998577],[40.41434000500004,-3.7051117059999115],[40.41450584900008,-3.7051892979999366],[40.41467624500007,-3.705247616999941],[40.41484988700006,-3.7052862129999085],[40.415025445000026,-3.7053047909998895],[40.41520157100007,-3.7053032079999184],[40.41537691600007,-3.7052814779999608],[40.415550136000036,-3.7052397659998633],[40.41571990400007,-3.705178389999901],[40.41579421800003,-3.70514207899987],[40.41952485500008,-3.7030698709999115],[40.41961154000006,-3.7030143699998916],[40.41987835000003,-3.7028197069998896],[40.419994522000025,-3.702718779999941],[40.42044353700004,-3.7022593969999207],[40.42055667900007,-3.7021668859998726],[40.421416012000066,-3.7016071369998826],[40.42145914900004,-3.701577099999895],[40.42350511700005,-3.7000578929998937],[40.42399460900003,-3.699721974999875],[40.42550595500006,-3.6987962989999232],[40.42553752300006,-3.6987759699999287],[40.42622577800006,-3.698310704999926],[40.426284973000065,-3.6982669069999474],[40.42680264900008,-3.6978493849999268],[40.42683450200008,-3.6978224689999024],[40.42798521000003,-3.696804509999879],[40.42802879800007,-3.696763419999911],[40.42845474000006,-3.696336070999905],[40.42849263800008,-3.6962958689998686],[40.429800518000036,-3.6948298989999557],[40.42983988300006,-3.694801577999897],[40.429880884000056,-3.6947775629998887],[40.42992324900007,-3.694758012999955],[40.42